node.title: Boy drowns in backyard pool in Adelaide's north
node.alt: An SA Ambulance Service sign on the side of a vehicle with another in the background saying Emergency Ambulance
node.description: A seven-year-old boy drowns in a swimming pool in Para Hills West.
node.content: ["A seven-year-old boy has drowned in a backyard swimming pool in Adelaide's north.", "Police said emergency services were called to a home on Goodfield Road about 6:30pm last night.", "The boy was unconscious when they arrived.", "Paramedics worked on the boy but he died at the scene.", "Police say there are no suspicious circumstances.", "They are preparing a report for the coroner."]
